Straight wins.

17:07.426 --> 17:09.060
£20,000.

17:13.733 --> 17:17.468
I've only got eight left,
all right? Just...

17:18.405 --> 17:20.637
Can't you stake me?

17:20.640 --> 17:23.107
- You pay tomorrow.
- Of course.

17:25.512 --> 17:27.178
Show me your cards.

17:39.526 --> 17:41.125
Royal flush wins.

17:44.197 --> 17:47.632
You owe me, tomorrow,
end of the day.

17:47.634 --> 17:50.068
£12,000.

17:50.070 --> 17:52.804
All right. Okay. Yeah.
Sure, I'll get your money.

17:54.274 --> 17:57.508
- Understand. I want my money tomorrow.
- All right.

18:34.414 --> 18:35.546
Are you all right?

18:37.150 --> 18:38.349
Yeah.

18:41.888 --> 18:44.455
I understand you're in trouble.

18:46.659 --> 18:49.293
We like to challenge fortune.

18:49.295 --> 18:52.430
But we also know
that the house always wins.

18:52.432 --> 18:54.165
Yeah, I guess.

18:54.167 --> 18:56.667
I, uh... I just had
a bit of bad luck, that's all.

18:56.669 --> 19:00.805
You didn't choose
your opponent wisely. Hmm?

19:01.574 --> 19:04.242
But, uh, I can help you.

19:05.245 --> 19:07.445
If you want me to.

19:07.447 --> 19:09.547
Why would you wanna help me?

19:09.549 --> 19:12.884
I invest in friendships.

19:12.886 --> 19:17.522
And I believe you can become
my trustworthy friend.

19:17.524 --> 19:20.324
I don't have myself down
as very trustworthy.

19:20.326 --> 19:21.726
My name is Lau.

19:27.834 --> 19:30.301
- And you are?
- Do you want me to help you?

19:31.204 --> 19:32.270
How?

19:32.805 --> 19:35.406
I'll pay the £12,000.

19:37.243 --> 19:38.643
But I need more than that.

19:38.645 --> 19:41.546
- How much?
- Another 50 grand.

19:42.882 --> 19:44.482
All right.

19:45.518 --> 19:47.952
Wait. What's the catch?

19:50.490 --> 19:53.457
Tomorrow, I want you to
take a flight to Amsterdam,

19:53.459 --> 19:56.794
and exchange this briefcase
for a suitcase.

19:57.764 --> 20:00.431
Then you can come back to London

20:00.433 --> 20:02.400
with that suitcase.

20:02.869 --> 20:04.669
You book a hotel.

20:04.671 --> 20:07.872
You text the address
to the number in this phone,

20:07.874 --> 20:10.541
and ditch the phone
in the canal.

20:11.578 --> 20:13.878
And at that particular address,

20:13.880 --> 20:17.582
somebody will contact you
for the exchange of the cases.

20:17.584 --> 20:21.352
- What's in the cases?
- It's better not to ask.

20:21.354 --> 20:24.956
You'll get a 6:00 a.m. flight
from Heathrow.

20:26.893 --> 20:28.492
And if I don't do it?

20:29.796 --> 20:32.363
Then we're not friends.

20:32.365 --> 20:35.700
You deal with
the consequences yourself.

20:38.004 --> 20:41.706
I pay Li the $12,000 now.

20:41.708 --> 20:45.309
And when you come back
with the suitcase,

20:45.311 --> 20:48.646
you will receive this £150,000.

20:48.648 --> 20:50.848
Plenty there to pay your debt.

20:53.886 --> 20:54.952
Okay.

20:59.759 --> 21:02.727
Oh. This man is my friend,

21:02.729 --> 21:06.397
so I take care of his debt now.

21:11.871 --> 21:14.538
We'll give you the briefcase
tomorrow morning.

21:14.540 --> 21:17.508
We'll get it through UK customs.

21:17.510 --> 21:20.278
But you have to deal
with Amsterdam security.

21:21.881 --> 21:23.814
If you lose this case,

21:23.816 --> 21:26.417
or the suitcase
that you pick up...

21:27.787 --> 21:30.354
your life will be on the line.

21:34.861 --> 21:36.027
Good luck.

21:43.002 --> 21:46.871
<i>♪ Chasing love</i>

21:46.873 --> 21:50.708
<i>♪ Losing love</i>

21:51.978 --> 21:54.812
<i>♪ Dying for love</i>

21:55.715 --> 21:57.915
<i>♪ In places</i>

21:57.917 --> 22:00.851
